<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.4">
<l>nāntakamēntiya nampicaraṇeṉṟu</l>
<l>tāḻnta taṉañcayaṟkāki taraṇiyil</l>
<l>vēntarkaḷuṭka vicayaṉmaṇittiṇtē</l>
<l>rūrntavaṉeṉṉaippuṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">umparkōṉeṉṉaippuṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who, for the sake of Dhanañjaya who prostrated,</l>
<l>[saying] “Nampi who holds the sword Nāntakam is the refuge,”</l>
<l>drove the solid, jewelled chariot of Vijaya</l>
<l>so that the kings upon the earth were terrified,</l>
<l>will embrace me from behind.</l>
<l>The king of celestials will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
